==Landscaping the land==
To show the toolbar press the landscape button [[File:en/Manual/Manual html m233f8633.png]] on the [[en/Manual/Game interface|menu bar]]. Once clicked the landscaping toolbar pops up (Fig 1).


<center>[[File:en/Manual/Landscaping toolbar.png|center|frame|Fig 1. - The Landscaping Toolbar]]</center>

==What do all those buttons do?==
The buttons are selfexplanatory. From left to right:<br>
:*[[File:en/Manual/Clear title.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Clear land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Manual/Lower land.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Lower land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Manual/Raise land.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Raise land]] button'''
:*[[File:en/Manual/Level land.png]] '''[[en/Manual/Landscaping|Level land]] button'''
