:*[[File:en/Manual/Place sign.png]] '''Place [[en/Archive/Manual/Signs|sign]] button'''

==How to level land==
If you want to flatten land over a large area you should use the level land button.

:#Start by clicking and holding down the mouse where you want to start.
:#*The height of the leveled land will be the same height as the tile you started on.<br><br>
:#Then drag the mouse over area you want to level.<br>[[File:en/Manual/Level land before.png|center|frame|View when an area is selected]]<br><br>
:#When satisfied with the area, release the button and the area should then be leveled.<br>[[File:en/Manual/Level land after.png|center|frame|View after the area has been leveled]]